# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Part 3e — Refined-scan surfaced (Hz + cross-ref + lineage + same-form)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Third scan in the autoresearch loop. The refined scoring lives in
# `scripts/scan_dyad_candidates.py` — for each candidate pair it
# composes four signals:
#
#   score = 1.0*cross_ref + 0.6*hz_proximity + 0.3*lineage_match + 0.4*same_form
#
# Two thresholds, because the two origins teach differently:
#   - Scan-discovered (no cross-ref in prose): score ≥ 1.0. The scan
#     PROPOSES candidates the prose has not yet noticed.
#   - Promoted (cross-ref already in prose): score ≥ 1.9. The body
#     ALREADY noticed; the scan's job is to TYPE the relation as
#     dyad-pair vs sequence/influence.
#
# Hz-proximity weighs same-band (1.0), named complementary bands
# (1.0 — e.g. 174↔963, 396↔528, 528↔741), or adjacent Solfeggio
# (0.3). Lineage-match: same texture (1.0), mixed (-0.5).
# Same-form: shared geometry.form (1.0).
#
# Four pairs survived the dyad-pair discernment from the top-10
# scan-discovered + a sweep of top-promoted. Six rejected; three held.
# Signal/noise this round: 4 confirmed / 10 assessed = 40%. Up from
# the cumulative 28.6% (PR #1987 + PR #1992). The refinement teaches
# the body to see better.
#
# Note on demotion: an earlier draft listed lc-awareness-as-self ↔
# lc-stillness as a fifth confirmed pair (membrane-crossing). On
# second read against the body's existing rows — Pair 4
# (lc-shared-hold ↔ lc-stillness, ground-event) and Pair 9
# (lc-awareness-as-self ↔ lc-freedom-as-recognition, ground-event)
# — both proposed cells are ground-poles of already-noticed ground-
# event pairs. Awareness-as-self ↔ stillness reads as equivalence
# (two names for one ground), not complementarity. Demoted to
# REJECT-9 below; the climb-to-50 in the first draft was the
# overcount that this honest read corrects.

# Pair 12 — substrate's freedom and its trace-charge
#
# lc-act-without-penalty (hz 396, tetrad, synthesized) — when every
# move is traceable to its originating recipe, no extra penalty layer
# is needed. The substrate's cost-shape IS the freedom-shape.
#
# lc-observer-pays-the-trace (hz 528, tetrad, synthesized) — the
# choice of base+recipe selects the graph AND charges the chooser;
# the observer cannot get out of paying for what observation costs.
#
# Same surface (substrate-as-economy), two complementary positions:
# act-without-penalty is the *freedom* this gives; observer-pays is
# the *mechanism* that makes the freedom honest. Neither alone:
# freedom without trace-charge becomes laissez-faire; trace-charge
# without freedom becomes surveillance. The teaching IS the bridge —
# the body can be free precisely because the trace charges itself.
defn pair_act_without_penalty_observer_pays = dyad_pair_shape {
    cell_a:      @concept(lc-act-without-penalty),
    cell_b:      @concept(lc-observer-pays-the-trace),
    kind:        kind_source_flow,
    axis:        "trace-economy",
    discernment: "substrate's freedom and its trace-charge — penalty-needed-no-more BECAUSE observer-pays-the-trace; mechanism makes the freedom honest, freedom is what the mechanism produces",
    noticed_at:  "2026-05-24",
    noticed_by:  "refined-scan-pr-current",
};

